Download TIGER shapes for Secondary School Districts

Source: R/secondary_school_districts.R
tt_secondary_school_districts.Rd

Download TIGER shapes for Secondary School Districts

Usage

tt_secondary_school_districts(state, year = 2021)

Arguments

state

FIPS, postal codes, or full names of states.

year

Integer year. Required. 2000 and 2010-2021 are currently supported.

Value

sf data.frame

Examples

# Wrapped in try due to false positive 304 errors
try(tt_secondary_school_districts("AZ"))
